name: Evelyn Rysdyk
what_you_do: Evelyn C. Rysdyk is an author, shamanic teacher, speaker, and healer who uses her work to inspire individuals to live joyful and purposeful lives through shamanism and healing practices.
who_you_serve: Evelyn serves individuals seeking personal growth, healing, and spiritual development, as well as groups and organizations looking for workshops and presentations on shamanism.
bio: Nationally recognized shaman teacher/healer, speaker, and author with over 40 years of experience in the arts and healing.
